just thinks it=E2=80=99s funnier to get out of the deal. I don=E2=80=99t kn=
ow.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The definitive merger agreemen=
t that Musk signed does not allow Musk to get out of the deal because he ch=
