<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Mr. Milton also said in interviews that the Ba=
dger was a =E2=80=9Cfully functioning vehicle inside and outside.=E2=80=9D =
When he was asked on Twitter when the first prototype would be produced, he=
