<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[2] There is an important caveat to this that =
I am going to put here because it is technical. Musk actually is *not* allo=
wed to terminate the agreement if *he* is =E2=80=9Cin material breach of an=
y of [his] representations, warranties, covenants or agreements=E2=80=9D un=
